\dedicatory{Revised version}

\begin{abstract}
I give a cohomological  characterization
of semiample line bundles. The result  is a 
generalization of both the Fujita--Zariski
Theorem on semiampleness  and the Grothendieck--Serre
Criterion for ampleness.
As an application of the Fujita--Zariski Theorem I
characterize  contractible curves
in 1-dimen\-sional families.
\end{abstract}

